\v 4 Então, <a name="03800400400008" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">perguntei</a> ao <a name="03800400400014" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">anjo</a> que <a name="03800400400018" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falava</a> comigo: <a name="03800400400030" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="03800400400030" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>, <a name="03800400400026" ll="SDBH:מָה:000000">que</a> é isto? 
