\v 6 <a name="03800400600004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">Prosseguiu</a> ele e me <a name="03800400600008" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Esta é a <a name="03800400600018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="03800400600020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="03800400600020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> a <a name="03800400600024" ll="SDBH:זְרֻבָּבֶל:000000">Zorobabel</a>: Não por <a name="03800400600034" ll="SDBH:חַיִל:000000">força</a> nem por <a name="03800400600042" ll="SDBH:כֹּחַ:000000">poder</a>, mas pelo <a name="03800400600050" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000000">meu</a> <a name="03800400600050" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000000">Espírito</a>, <a name="03800400600052" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="03800400600054" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="03800400600056" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">dos</a> <a name="03800400600056" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">Exércitos</a>. 
\v 7 Quem és tu, ó <a name="03800400700010" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000000">grande</a> <a name="03800400700006" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">monte</a>? <a name="03800400700014">Diante</a> de <a name="03800400700016" ll="SDBH:זְרֻבָּבֶל:000000">Zorobabel</a> serás uma <a name="03800400700020" ll="SDBH:מִישֹׁור:000000">campina</a>; porque <a name="03800400700024" ll="SDBH:יצא:000001">ele</a> <a name="03800400700024" ll="SDBH:יצא:000001">colocará</a> a <a name="03800400700030" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000007" il="Realia:1.8.4c;il_quarry_transport_d01;jlm_quarrying_d01" tl="HOTTP4437">pedra</a> de <a name="03800400700034" ll="SDBH:רֹאשָׁה:000000" tl="HOTTP4437">remate</a>, em meio a <a name="03800400700036" ll="SDBH:תְּשֻׁאָה:000000">aclamações</a>: Haja <a name="03800400700038" ll="SDBH:חֵן:000000">graça</a> e <a name="03800400700040" ll="SDBH:חֵן:000000">graça</a> para ela!
    
\v 8 Novamente, me veio a <a name="03800400800006" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="03800400800008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="03800400800008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="03800400800014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: 
\v 9 As <a name="03800400900002">mãos</a> de <a name="03800400900004" ll="SDBH:זְרֻבָּבֶל:000000">Zorobabel</a> <a name="03800400900006" ll="SDBH:יסד:000000">lançaram</a> <a name="03800400900006" ll="SDBH:יסד:000000">os</a> <a name="03800400900006" ll="SDBH:יסד:000000">fundamentos</a> desta <a name="03800400900010" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="304, Temple Mount;Bolen00063;LB00248;Realia:3.14.1.2;Realia:3.14.1a;jlm_herod_temple_court_e_m01;jlm_herod_temple_court_women_m01;jlm_herod_temple_d01;jlm_herod_temple_golden_vine_m01;jlm_herod_temple_m01;jlm_herod_temple_plan_d01;jlm_herod_tm_nw_m01;jlm_herod_tm_se_m02">casa</a>, <a name="03800400900018">elas</a> <a name="03800400900018">mesmas</a> a <a name="03800400900020" ll="SDBH:בצע:000004">acabarão</a>, para que <a name="03800400900024">saibais</a> que o <a name="03800400900028" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> dos <a name="03800400900030" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">Exércitos</a> <a name="03800400900032" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">é</a> <a name="03800400900032" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">quem</a> <a name="03800400900032" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">me</a> <a name="03800400900032" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">enviou</a> a vós outros. 
\v 10 Pois quem <a name="03800401000006" ll="SDBH:בוז:000000">despreza</a> o <a name="03800401000010" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">dia</a> dos <a name="03800401000012" ll="SDBH:קָטָן:000003">humildes</a> <a name="03800401000012" ll="SDBH:קָטָן:000003">começos</a>, esse <a name="03800401000016" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">alegrar</a>-<a name="03800401000016" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">se</a>-<a name="03800401000016" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">á</a> <a name="03800401000020" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vendo</a> o <a name="03800401000026;03800401000030" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000001;SDBH:בְּדִיל:000001" il="HK00126;LB00125;tb041105516" tl="HOTTP4438">prumo</a> na <a name="03800401000034">mão</a> de <a name="03800401000036" ll="SDBH:זְרֻבָּבֶל:000000">Zorobabel</a>. Aqueles <a name="03800401000038" ll="SDBH:שֶׁבַע:000000">sete</a> olhos são os <a name="03800401000042" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> do <a name="03800401000044" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, que <a name="03800401000048" ll="SDBH:שׁוט:000000">percorrem</a> toda a <a name="03800401000056" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>.
    
\v 11 <a name="03800401100004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">Prossegui</a> e lhe <a name="03800401100008" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">perguntei</a>: que são as <a name="03800401100014" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">duas</a> <a name="03800401100018" ll="SDBH:זַיִת:000000" il="Gethsemane389;LB00087;NBGbs20090227 1_31;NBGbs20090227-1_61;tb052816082">oliveiras</a> à <a name="03800401100026" ll="SDBH:יָמִין:000000">direita</a> e à <a name="03800401100036" ll="SDBH:שְׂמֹאל:000000">esquerda</a> do <a name="03800401100030" ll="SDBH:מְנֹורָה:000000" il="NBGlo20140124;NBGlo20140127;NBGlo20140127a;NBGlo20140504d;Realia:4.3.4a;Realia:4.3.4b;Realia:5.2b;il_tabernacle_holy_incense_veil_m30">candelabro</a>? 
\v 12 <a name="03800401200006" ll="SDBH:שֵׁנִי:000000">Tornando</a> a <a name="03800401200004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">falar</a>-lhe, <a name="03800401200010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">perguntei</a>: que são aqueles <a name="03800401200016" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> <a name="03800401200018" ll="SDBH:שִׁבֹּלֶת:001001">raminhos</a> de <a name="03800401200022" ll="SDBH:זַיִת:000000" il="LB00087;NBGbs20090227 1_31;NBGbs20090227-1_61">oliveira</a> que estão <a name="03800401200028" ll="SDBH:יָד:000026">junto</a> aos <a name="03800401200030" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> <a name="03800401200032" ll="SDBH:צַנְתְּרֹות:000000">tubos</a> de <a name="03800401200036" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000000" il="Bolen00041;Bolen00050;Bolen00053;adr1006039110;adr1305240906;adr1306212575">ouro</a>, que vertem de si azeite <a name="03800401200048" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000000" il="Bolen00041;Bolen00050;Bolen00053;adr1006039110;adr1305240906;adr1306212575" tl="HOTTP4439">dourado</a>? 
\v 13 Ele me <a name="03800401300004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">respondeu</a>: Não <a name="03800401300016">sabes</a> <a name="03800401300018" ll="SDBH:מָה:000000">que</a> é isto? Eu <a name="03800401300024" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: não, <a name="03800401300028" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="03800401300028" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>. 
\v 14 Então, ele <a name="03800401400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: São os <a name="03800401400008" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> <a name="03800401400010;03800401400012;03800401400014" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000007;SDBH:יִצְהָר:000000" il="Fauna:2.28;NBGbs20100214-0211;NBGbs20110227-41;NBGbs20110227-42;NBGpb20140124a;NBGpb20140204;Olives in press, rp;RS26272_ISR91T-117;il_oil_press_d01">ungidos</a>, que <a name="03800401400018">assistem</a> junto ao <a name="03800401400022" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">Senhor</a> de toda a <a name="03800401400028" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>.
\c 5
\v 1 <a name="03800500100004" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000041">Tornei</a> a <a name="03800500100008" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000039">levantar</a> <a name="03800500100010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">os</a> <a name="03800500100010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> e <a name="03800500100014" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vi</a>, e eis um <a name="03800500100020" ll="SDBH:מְגִלָּה:000000" il="NBGpb20140728b;Realia:1.7.1a;Realia:3.13.8;Torah">rolo</a> <a name="03800500100022" ll="SDBH:עוף:000000">voante</a>. 
