<a name="03801401000076" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>. 
\v 11 <a name="03801401100004">Habitarão</a> nela, e já não haverá <a name="03801401100010" ll="SDBH:חֵרֶם:001001">maldição</a>, e <a name="03801401100022" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_nehemiah_d02;jlm_nehemiah_m02_ann;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a> <a name="03801401100020">habitará</a> <a name="03801401100026" ll="SDBH:בֶּטַח:000000">segura</a>.
    
